<li>Doke, C.M. (1958) <i>Zulu-English Vocabulary</i>. Johannesburg: Witwatersrand University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/085494009X" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-85494-009-X</a></li>
