<li><span class="citation book">Colenso, John William (1882). <a href="http://www.archive.org/details/firststepsinzulu00coleuoft" class="external text" rel="nofollow"><i>First steps in Zulu: being an elementary grammar of the Zulu language</i></a> (Third ed.). Martizburg, Durban: Davis<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.archive.org/details/firststepsinzulu00coleuoft" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.archive.org/details/firststepsinzulu00coleuoft</a></span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=First+steps+in+Zulu%3A+being+an+elementary+grammar+of+the+Zulu+language&amp;rft.aulast=Colenso&amp;rft.aufirst=John+William&amp;rft.au=Colenso%2C%26%2332%3BJohn+William&amp;rft.date=1882&amp;rft.edition=Third&amp;rft.place=Martizburg%2C+Durban&amp;rft.pub=Davis&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.archive.org%2Fdetails%2Ffirststepsinzulu00coleuoft&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Zulu_language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
